<p>We'd also like to take a minute to survey about your involvement with the
Perl Mongers in your area.   Many people do not know that there are many Perl
Monger groups located all over the world.   Membership in the Perl Mongers is
free.</p>

<div class="survey-question">Are you already involved with a Perl Monger group? (If not, why?)</div>
